<font color="#FF0000">HOLY SPAM!</font><br>
<tt>Sun Aug 24 22:26:15 US/Eastern 1997
</tt><p>
Horror and madness is hard to meet,<br>
but you can get it done if you have Spam to eat.<br>
Welcome home Brother! is a fine way to greet, <br>
but its a hollow reception.. without Spam to eat.<br>
So.. when I die and make the final retreat,<br>
I hope the Lamb's feast includes.. Spam to eat.<br>
The Devil had issued this omninous threat<br>
(both to me and my brother &quot;No Sweat Chet)<br>
that if we are to live for eternity without regret,<br>
we must change our evil ways at God's sainted feet<br>
...&quot;cause heaven is filled with Spam to eat!&quot;<br><br>
